                  -- H A R D   D I S K    I N S T A L L --
                  
                  Ooops, sorry, cant be bothered to write
                  a hard disk installer for this one. You
                  can install it by hand though by copying
                 "hop-shop.exe" and the "hungry" directory
                 to your hard disk. Double-click to load
                 or CD to the dir and type "hop-shop.exe".
                  If it just sits at the loading screen
                 looking stupid then you dont have enough
                 memory, try killing some stuff before it
                  next time....                
